Class TupleMaker

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.lcsim.util.Driver
      • org.hps.analysis.tuple.TupleMaker
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FEETupleDriver, MCTupleMaker, MollerTupleDriver, RefitTrackTruthTupleDriver, TridentTupleDriver, WABTupleDriver

    public abstract class TupleMaker
extends Driver
    sort of an interface for DQM analysis drivers creates the DQM database manager, checks whether row exists in db etc calculateEndOfRunQuantities & printDQMData i.e. useful methods
